<p>Olivia Jade has tied to lead a quieter life in the two years since her parents were busted in the bribery scam to get their children into USC but earlier this month her boyfriend of two years landed in his own legal troubles.</p>

<p>Guthy, 24, was booked for misdemeanor driving under the influence after he was pulled over in California on September 7, Us Weekly reported Tuesday.</p>

<p>Guthy was busted behind the wheel in Santa Monica around 3.13pm and was released from custody at 7.28pm, booking records show. </p>

